{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"密码","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Cipher","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>在密码学（<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cryptography\">cryptography <small>(en-US)</small></a>）领域，<strong>密码</strong>是将<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Plaintext\">明文</a><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Encryption\">编码</a>为不可读，且能够<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Decryption\">解码</a>回原来的明文的算法。</p>\n<p>在信息时代很久以前，密码就已经很常见了（例如<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9B%BF%E6%8D%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">替换密码</a>和<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-cn/%E5%8F%A4%E5%85%B8%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81#%E7%A7%BB%E4%BD%8D%E5%BC%8F%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">移位密码</a>），但是它们之中除了<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-cn/%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%80%A7%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81%E6%9C%AC\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">一次性密码本</a>以外，其他的均不满足密码学上的安全性。</p>\n<p>现代密码通常为抵抗<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cryptanalysis\">密码分析学家 <small>(en-US)</small></a>的<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此文档尚未被撰写，期待你的贡献!\">攻击</a>设计。不能保证所有攻击的方法都能被发现，但是每个算法也经历了很多已知攻击手段的检验。</p>\n<p>密码通常以两种方式工作，或者在连续的数据块、缓冲区中作为<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-cn/%E5%88%86%E7%BB%84%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">分块密码</a>使用，或者在数据流（通常是音频或视频流）中作为<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-cn/%E6%B5%81%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">流密码</a>使用。</p>\n<p>密码以处理<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Key\">密钥</a>的方式不同可以分为两类：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-cn/%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E5%AF%86%E9%92%A5%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">对称密钥加密算法</a>使用同样的密钥进行消息的加密和解密。如果消息有保密性需求，那么密钥也应该进行安全的传送。</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-cn/%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%80%E5%AF%86%E9%92%A5%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">非对称密钥加密算法</a>使用不同的密钥进行消息的加密和解密。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>维基百科上的<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-cn/%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">密码</a>词条</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Archive/Security/Encryption_and_Decryption\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">加密与解密</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary\">MDN 术语表</a>\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Block_cipher_mode_of_operation\">Block cipher mode of operation</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Cipher\" aria-current=\"page\">密码</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Ciphertext\">密文</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Cipher_suite\">密码套件</a></li>\n      <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cryptanalysis\">密码分析 <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n      <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cryptography\">密码学 <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Decryption\">解密</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Encryption\">加密</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Key\">密钥</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Plaintext\">明文</a></li>\n      <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Public-key_cryptography\">非对称密钥算法 <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n      <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Symmetric-key_cryptography\">对称密钥算法 <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"在密码学（cryptography (en-US)）领域，密码是将明文编码为不可读，且能够解码回原来的明文的算法。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Cipher","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Algoritmo criptográfico","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Chiffre","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Cipher (サイファー)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/cipher","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/cipher/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Cipher","title":"密码"}],"pageTitle":"密码 - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}